                        <span class="fal fa-fw fa-handshake fa-5x"> </span>
                        <p>
                            <strong>1/4<br />
                            <a href="http://www.volunteerscotland.net/policy-and-research/">More than a quarter of Scottish adults volunteered in 2016</a></strong>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mdc-layout-grid__cell mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-3-desktop mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-4-tablet mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-4-phone">
